00:08:57,864 --> 00:08:59,764
Fine.

248
00:08:59,799 --> 00:09:01,032
But you better be careful.

249
00:09:01,067 --> 00:09:02,278
Because if
you're looking at Gibbs,

250
00:09:02,302 --> 00:09:03,601
