255
00:09:13,646 --> 00:09:15,980
Gentlemen, thank you
for meeting with me

256
00:09:16,015 --> 00:09:17,648
on such short notice.
Our pleasure.

257
00:09:17,684 --> 00:09:19,361
I assume you looked through
the documents I sent over

